data.description: Welcome to this stunning home in the desirable Lakeview neighborhood of Jackson, GA. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and approximately 2000 sqft of living space, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality.  Step inside and be greeted by the impeccable interior features that are sure to impress. The kitchen, adorned with quartz countertops, is a chef's dream and will make meal preparation a breeze. The huge master suite is a true retreat, providing a sanctuary to unwind after a long day. With a bonus room, there is plenty of space for a home office, playroom, or whatever your heart desires. The two additional bedrooms are conveniently located opposite the master bedroom, offering privacy and tranquility.  This home is equipped with a wired camera system complete with a DVR and monitor, providing you with peace of mind and added security.  The exterior of this home is just as exceptional as the interior. The 12x20 outbuilding, 12x18carport, and 2-car garage provide ample storage space for all your belongings. The shed is perfect for housing your tools and equipment. And the expansive covered rear porch is the ideal spot to relax and enjoy the serene surroundings.  Situated in the sought-after Lakeview neighborhood, this home offers a prime location. High Falls Lake is less than 1 mile away, offering endless opportunities for boating, fishing, and water sports. High Falls State Park is just a short 5-minute drive away, providing hiking trails, camping, and breathtaking scenery. Additionally, this home is served by the highly regarded Monroe County schools, ensuring an excellent education for your children.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this dream home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and convenience of Lakeview living in Jackson, GA.
